d reliability without going to either extreme.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:6px 0;\"><strong>Consider the alternative if:</strong> If you want the strongest review track record, the top-rated pick above may be a safer bet.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin:6px 0;\"><strong>Value for money:</strong> Mid-pack pricing relative to the other options compared here.</p>\n  </div>\n</div></div>\n<div style=\"background:#f5f0ff;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:24px 0;\">\n  <h3 style=\"margin-top:0;\">Final Recommendation</h3>\n  <div class=\"cr-verdict-picks\" style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:16px 0;\">\n    <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:220px;background:#fff;border-radius:10px;padding:16px;text-align:center;\">\n      <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/images/img-70.jpg\" alt=\"ENGPOW File Box with Lock,Fireproof Document Box with Zipper＆Pockets,Collapsible File Organizer Filing Storage Cabinet with Handle,Portable Home Office Safe for Hanging Letter/Legal Folder,Black Global Recycled Standard Global Recycled Standard Global Recycled Standard\" style=\"width:140px;height:140px;object-fit:contain;background:#fff;border-radius:8px;\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n      <p style=\"margin:10px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Best overall:</strong> #3 ENGPOW File Box with Lock</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:14px;color:#555;\">the strongest rating/review combination in this comparison.</p>\n      <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08D6JLTXJ?tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer sponsored\" style=\"background:#8920F3;color:#fff;padding:10px 18px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;display:inline-block;\">Buy on Amazon USA &rarr;</a>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:220px;background:#fff;border-radius:10px;padding:16px;text-align:center;\">\n      <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/images/img-70.jpg\" alt=\"ENGPOW File Box with Lock,Fireproof Document Box with Zipper＆Pockets,Collapsible File Organizer Filing